{"article_id":"UxkzJci1zvW0B1Al","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In the wake of the Supreme Court ' s ruling last week ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"Republicans on Capitol Hill spent four days laying out an attack on President Obama ' s health care law as a massive tax increase .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Eric Fehrnstrom said","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Mr. Romney agrees with Mr. Obama","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that the law ' s punishment","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"for flouting the individual mandate","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"and not buying health insurance","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"is a \" penalty , \" not a tax","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"- just like the legislation","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Mr. Romney signed as governor of Massachusetts .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"\" The governor has consistently described the mandate in Massachusetts as a penalty , \"","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Mr. Fehrnstrom said on MSNBC .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"\" The governor disagreed with the ruling of the court ;","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"he agreed with the dissent","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"that was written by Justice","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"[ Antonin ]","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"Scalia ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"which clearly states","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"the mandate was not a tax . \"","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"After watching the court reject their legal arguments ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"congressional Republicans settled for what they hoped would be a powerful political attack ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"bolstered by the court ' s declaration","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that the individual mandate amounted to a tax .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"The court ' s conclusion contradicted Mr. Obama ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"who during the debate in 2009 and 2010 had repeatedly said","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"it wasn ' t a tax .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" The court has now spoken .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"It is a tax , \"","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell , Kentucky Republican , said in the aftermath of the ruling .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"The National Republican Congressional Committee began issuing press releases","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"using the court-approved tax argument","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"to attack Democrats .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"After Mr. Fehrnstrom ' s comments Monday , however , activists said","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"they had been undercut .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"\" We did not like Obamacare to start with","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"now that the Supreme Court has called it a tax ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"it gave Romney the room","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"to run straight for a touchdown , \"","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Tea Party Nation founder Judson Phillips wrote on the group ' s blog .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" What kind of idiots are running the Romney campaign ?","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Instead of spiking the football","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"and winning ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"the Romney campaign has just turned over the ball . \"","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"He wondered","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"whether it was too late for the GOP to have a brokered convention","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"and replace Mr. Romney as its presidential nominee .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"\" One - it was a stupid thing to say , \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"said Ben Marchi , former director of the Virginia chapter of the anti-tax group Americans for Prosperity .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"\" At the end of the day ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"whether you call it a tax or a fee ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"it means more money out of working Americans ' pockets in tough economic times .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"People","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"who don ' t have jobs right now","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"don ' t care","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"whether you call it a tax or a fee . \"","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Still , he hoped","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"conservatives would rally to Mr. Romney anyway .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" Conservatives don ' t trust him","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"because he ' s the author of Romneycare .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Conservatives trust him","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"because he ' s pledged to repeal Obamacare , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Mr. Marchi said .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Mr. McConnell ' s office didn ' t address the conflicting Republican messages ,","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"choosing instead to focus on an area","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"where the Senate minority leader agreed with Mr. Romney :","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"\" The Supreme Court should have ruled Obamacare unconstitutional , \"","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"a spokesman said .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Mr. Romney signed a health law in Massachusetts","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that included a mandate , similar to the Obama reforms ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"requiring everyone to buy insurance","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"- and imposing a fine on those","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"who didn ' t .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg even cited Mr. Romney ' s law as backing for the national law in her concurring opinion last week .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"But Mr. Romney has vowed to repeal the federal law ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"it goes beyond the powers of the federal government","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"and saying","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"states should be left to experiment .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"At this point Mr. Romney and Mr. Obama agree","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"that the mandate is not a tax","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"- putting them in opposition to congressional Republicans .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"But Mr. Romney and Mr. Obama disagree over whether the law is constitutional .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Mr. Romney won backing from some GOP quarters .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Virginia Attorney General Kenneth T. Cuccinelli II ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"who filed one of the key lawsuits against the national health care law ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"told The","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"that Mr. Romney is correct","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"to argue","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"that the penalty isn ' t a tax .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"\" They upheld the law","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"by expanding any known definition of the taxing power very dramatically , \"","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"Mr. Cuccinelli said .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"\" For those","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"who want to deny","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"it ' s a tax ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"then they have to essentially concede","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"that it ' s unconstitutional under any other power . \"","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"The Romney campaign also tried to frame the issue as a problem for Mr. Obama .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"\" The Supreme Court left President Obama with two choices :","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"The federal individual mandate in Obamacare is either a constitutional tax or an unconstitutional penalty , \"","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"spokeswoman Amanda Henneberg said .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"\" Gov . Romney thinks","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"it is an unconstitutional penalty .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"What is President Obama ' s position :","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Is his federal mandate unconstitutional","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"or is it a tax ? \"","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"During the primary election campaign , Mr. Romney ' s opponents attacked him as the wrong messenger for Republicans to take into a general election battle","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"they hoped","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"would make a referendum on the health care law .","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"Those opponents said","depth":4},{"id":112,"text":"Mr. Romney , as the man","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"who signed an individual mandate plan in Massachusetts ,","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"didn ' t have the credibility","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"to attack Mr. Obama .","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"\" Romney ' s team still hasn ' t solved their most fundamental problem","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"- how to attack Obama ' s health care policies","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"while continuing to embrace their own , \"","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"said Matt Latimer , a speechwriter for President George W. Bush administration","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"who briefly advised Newt Gingrich ' s presidential campaign .","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"\" Mr . Romney ' s primary opponents warned all along","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"that the governor ' s own record on health care would make him a flawed candidate , \"","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"Mr Latimer said .","depth":5},{"id":124,"text":"\" His campaign ' s remarks today ,","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"totally undercutting the Republican line of attack on Obamacare ,","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"only prove that point . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":253,"left":233,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":155,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":128,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":144,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":2,"right":143,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":143,"left":134,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":132,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":3,"right":131,"relation":"